1        Albania        "        http://www.parlament.al/"        Information on MPs' personal staff identity                24        MPs        1991        2014        Not online        not exist                                                                                Albanian MPs do not have personal staff at the moment. The staff of the Parliament serves the MPs but none of them has personal staff assigned. There\'s a reform going on at the moment regarding this and MPs will soon have offices and staff in their electoral areas (at the moment they only have an office at the Parliament) but these offices will serve all MPs elected from one political party in the area and not individual MPs since the electoral system is proportional regional and not majority. .
